    section.container.flex-grow
      .row
        .col-md-9.order-md-2.pt-2
          h2 Content.
          |  If you feel content, you're satisfied and happy. The content of a book, movie, or song is what it's about: the topic. This word has two main meanings. The first has to do with being pleased and satisfied (feeling content) or making someone
          |             else feel happy and at peace with things (contenting them). The other meaning has to do with subject matter: the content of a history class might be American history. The content of a math class might be geometry. As long as there's a topic
          |             or subject, there's content. Sssshhhh, no one cares.
        .col-md-3.order-md-1.pt-3
